--Grimlock, Slag, Swoop, Snarl, Sludge, Thunderwing--

Grimlock, Slag, Snarl, and Sludge walk beside Bluestreak and Ratchet 
with Thunderwing and Swoop flying over head.

Snarl asks Bluestreak and Ratchet, "How long of have you been on 
Earth?"

Swoop thens sees Shocker, Prowl, Iron Raptor fighting near the Ark.

Swoop tells his leader Grimlock, "Grimlock, looks like trouble at the 
Ark."

Swoop takes off towards the Ark with Thunderwing behind when Swoop 
transforms into robot mode and starts shooting his hand gun at 
Shocker.
